item.title: Tesla tops $1 billion in profit, delays Semi launch
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description:
Tesla Inc.s profit topped $1 billion for the first time in the company’s history and its sales nearly doubled, zooming past Wall Street expectations, but there was no stock rally late Monday as limited battery supply and the ongoing chip shortage crimped the Silicon Valley electric-car makers output and forced it to delay the launch […]
